{"tid":1489702,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"話說818個日遇到鬼 大家係用咁既方式趕走佢","createTime":"2019-08-20T02:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T02:41:07.000Z","uid":182439,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"aab03d391fa079692d684cc6170a7b4b6b2ee8d5","tid":1489702,"uid":182439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:37:19.000Z","msg":"離開左維園向住銅鑼灣方向走既個條路 <br />\n我地遇到隻疑似鬼<br />\n行行下個陣後面有位男士好大聲咁話我隔離個男人係鬼<br />\n仲講埋佢叫咩名同以前讀邊間中學<br />\n<br />\n隻疑似鬼既打扮當然同遊行人士冇分辨<br />\n黑衫黑褲 不過就戴太陽眼鏡同著住件銀色反光風褸<br />\n<br />\n一聽到佢係疑似鬼<br />\n所有人幾逼都好都即刻散遠啲同佢保持距離<br />\n個個都細細聲咁討論佢<br />\n再用啲憎恨既眼神望實佢<br />\n<br />\n而隻疑似鬼冇講任何一句野去反駁<br />\n淨係望住我地繼續行<br />\n<br />\n搞到佢走又走唔到 但係又要被人知佢身份<br />\n最重點係我地冇用任何暴力行為<br />\n連言語暴力都冇<br />\n<br />\n冇幾耐隻疑似鬼就自己靜靜雞咁係條小路到離開左遊行隊伍"},{"pid":"997e7e1a62404b27335950fb8143f36bf4df6c77","tid":1489702,"uid":182439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:37:48.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"cd8a47e0bf91f82f98846a3cef7ed9ba9f951ab0","tid":1489702,"uid":182439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:38:13.000Z","msg":"自推9次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32eece31a6223609c251ee814731b271b005b30e","tid":1489702,"uid":182439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:38:29.000Z","msg":"自推8次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96feda5803fdc1299a283fd1732b66df0a522ce","tid":1489702,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:38:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1d858932c0eba6c6f13b04b06ab83e6957390dc","tid":1489702,"uid":182439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:38:42.000Z","msg":"自推7次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f062c8f382b18ab576c71ada50712d59c87ea387","tid":1489702,"uid":182439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:38:57.000Z